if exists(select 1 from sys.sysforeignkey where role='FK_MPS_REGI_PRIJAVLJE_MPS_ORGA') then
alter table MPS_REGISTAR_ZAPOSLENIH
delete foreign key FK_MPS_REGI_PRIJAVLJE_MPS_ORGA
end if;

alter table MPS_REGISTAR_ZAPOSLENIH
add constraint FK_MPS_REGI_PRIJAVLJE_MPS_ORGA foreign key (PS_ID, VO_OZNAKA, DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, NM_DENTIFIKATOR, OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR)
references MPS_ORGANIZACIONE_JEDINICE (PS_ID, VO_OZNAKA, DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, NM_DENTIFIKATOR, OJ_IDENTIFIKATOR)
on update restrict
on delete restrict;
